          %pre
            %code
              :preserve
                setInterval(function() {
                  ... some code ...
                }, 500)
          %p
            Or you can pass it a reference to an existing function:
          %pre
            %code
              :preserve
                function myFunction() {
                  ... some code ...
                }

                setInterval(myFunction, 500);
          %p
            In this case the function will be called as if you ran
